Package org.bluezoo.gumdrop.telemetry

Interface TelemetryExporter

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    OTLPExporter
    public interface TelemetryExporter
    Interface for exporting trace, log, and metric data. Implementations may send data to an OpenTelemetry Collector, log to a file, or export to other observability backends.
    Author:
    Chris Burdess
